# AI Bug Report Assistant

## Overview

AI-powered tool that converts raw issue descriptions into structured, professional bug reports.

---

## Problem

Writing bug reports manually is repetitive and time-consuming, and testers may miss important details under pressure.

---

## Solution

This tool allows QA engineers to:

* Enter a simple issue description
* Generate a complete, structured bug report instantly

---

## Features

* Generate bug reports from plain text
* Structured output:

  * Title
  * Steps to Reproduce
  * Expected Result
  * Actual Result
  * Severity & Priority
* Environment selection (Platform, OS, Browser)
* Input validation to prevent empty or weak reports
* Copy-ready output for Jira / Azure DevOps

---

## Tech Stack

* Frontend: React + Vite + Tailwind
* Backend: Node.js + Express
* AI: Mock AI (ready for OpenAI integration)

---

## How to Run

### Frontend

npm install
npm run dev

### Backend

cd backend
npm install
node server.js

---

## Example

Input:
"Login button not working after clicking"

Output:

* Title: Login functionality not working
* Steps: Navigate → Enter credentials → Click login → Observe result
* Severity: High

---

## Author

Built by a QA Engineer to improve bug reporting workflows using modern AI concepts.
